<title>USA: Neuberger &amp; Berman Guardian sets qtly div.</title>
<headline>Neuberger &amp; Berman Guardian sets qtly div.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Neuberger &amp; Berman Guardian Trust said it declared a quarterly dividend of $0.01 per share which was lower than the prior dividend of $0.05 per share.</p>
<p>The company said that the last dividend of its fiscal year is usually different than its regular quarterly dividend.</p>
<p>The latest dividend is payable on March 27 to shareholders of record on March 27.</p>
